{"tid":1851290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屈臣氏間間都逼爆人排隊","createTime":"2020-01-30T03:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T04:06:45.000Z","uid":229794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"080e9ed45c6980288af29280bb578130ad6ab217","tid":1851290,"uid":229794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有冇巴絲打可以同仲排緊隊既人講<br />\n每一間分店既口罩真係<span style=\"color: red;\">少量</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">而且每間貨量都唔一樣</span><br />\n佢地得<span style=\"color: red;\">20</span>個籌 派完就冇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你手上冇籌既就唔洗排隊 <br />\n因為真係冇咁多貨比咁多分店</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc238a3c336d6b34c8487ccec43ed694fbd0dd51","tid":1851290,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"咪由鳩班廢老排隊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea1bc1a63107d609d455f379fb89f06dcd488da","tid":1851290,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻暴政</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"45710ce356d5eeb1d70f2da55550f5a687c52a63","tid":1851290,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr